Abstract = {{Dasypoda bees are host-specialized solitary species distributed in the
   Palaearctic Region. In the framework of a global revision of this genus,
   comprehensive descriptions of three rare species (D. tibialis Morawitz,
   D. vulpecula Lebedev and D. iberica Warncke) are presented. The detailed
